headline: Regional Management Shares Plunge 9.3% Despite Q3 Earnings Beat
summary: RM's third-quarter earnings benefit from rising interest and fee income and improved efficiency ratio. The hurricane impact, coupled with declining net insurance income, partially offset the results.

headline: Encore Capital Q3 Earnings Miss Estimates on Lower Purchases by Cabot
summary: ECPG's third-quarter earnings suffer from rising operating expenses and the competitive environment in the U.K. Improved portfolio purchasing in the United States partially offset the negatives.
